title: Mommy & Daddy 'find' infant daughter dead, call lawyer before 911!
itunes:title: Mommy & Daddy 'find' infant daughter dead, call lawyer before 911!
description:
Little Mary Welch died of neglect and starvation, but her father admitted to an emergency dispatcher that he called his lawyer for advice before dialing 911 after finding the baby dead in her bed. Seth Welch and his wife Tatiana Fusari now face murder charged for their daughter's death. The 10-month-old girl reportedly weighed only 8 pounds at the time of her death. Nancy Grace looks at the case with psycho analyst Dr. Bethany Marshall, juvenile judge & lawyer Ashley Willcott, private investigator Vincent Hill, and Crime Stories reporter John Lemley.
